    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在《汽车服务模拟器》中经营属于你自己的维修中心！</strong><br>真实的维修过程、细致的车辆改装、战略管理系统，以及可探索的动态开放世界尽在其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修车、改装、清洗、服务客户，打造属于你的汽车维修帝国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/b829bb79b88957cc8ba78269a0ba1cc6.poster.avif?t=1755268940\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/b829bb79b88957cc8ba78269a0ba1cc6.webm?t=1755268940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/b829bb79b88957cc8ba78269a0ba1cc6.mp4?t=1755268940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔧 <strong>主要特色</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>真实的车辆维修和保养体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修复引擎、刹车、悬挂和变速箱。使用专业工具应对各种复杂问题，成长为行业专家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/23fec1bd2b77366e6f89c5f12bb70315.poster.avif?t=1755268940\" width=792 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/23fec1bd2b77366e6f89c5f12bb70315.webm?t=1755268940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/23fec1bd2b77366e6f89c5f12bb70315.mp4?t=1755268940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>车辆个性化与性能提升</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计喷漆图案，添加车身套件与性能部件，提升车辆外观与操控性能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/36ebb56f334d85bce84c39978f719293.poster.avif?t=1755268940\" width=792 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/36ebb56f334d85bce84c39978f719293.webm?t=1755268940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/36ebb56f334d85bce84c39978f719293.mp4?t=1755268940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管理并扩大你的维修店</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与客户协商价格，制定策略并投资设备，实现收益最大化。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>专业的洗车服务</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过精细的清洁让车辆焕然一新，提高客户满意度并获得额外收入。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/f9932740d084eb3dabadf9d112f8017b.poster.avif?t=1755268940\" width=800 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/f9932740d084eb3dabadf9d112f8017b.webm?t=1755268940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062160/extras/f9932740d084eb3dabadf9d112f8017b.mp4?t=1755268940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战略决策推动成功</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >倾听客户反馈，制定合适方案，提升品牌信誉与盈利能力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索互动开放世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在废料场寻找稀有零件、探索市场或在线采购高端配件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造你的梦想维修车间，登顶汽车行业！</strong><br>立即将《汽车服务模拟器》加入愿望清单！</p>",
